Invocation Name: server name suggester
des:
Get a random server name suggestion.

It can be tough to think up of a name for your server so let this skill come up with one for you.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Server Name Suggestor" or "Alexa, open Server Name Suggestor" to get a server name suggestion.
Say "Another" or "Next" to get another random suggestion.

At any time, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
